title: Twilight for the Gods [1958 - USA] (Rock Hudson) drama
description:
Twilight for the Gods (1958 - USA)

Drama

starring . . . . Rock Hudson, Cyd Charisse, Arthur Kennedy
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0052326/


Filmed at Hawaii, USA

After being court-martialed and discharged from the Navy, Captain Bell turns to drink. Reduced to skippering a rundown schooner in the South Seas he takes on board a disparate group of passengers and crew including; a Honolulu prostitute on the lam, a third-rate show-biz entrepreneur, an ineffectual missionary, a washed-up opera star, and a couple of refugees. During a treacherous storm at sea, the true characters of all on board are revealed - for better or worse.
